statements: SELECT * FROM election_results;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, votes_received FROM election_results;
SELECT election_year, candidate_name, votes_received FROM election_results ORDER BY election_year DESC;
SELECT * FROM election_results WHERE party_affiliation = 'Democratic';
SELECT candidate_name, votes_received FROM election_results WHERE votes_received > 1000 ORDER BY votes_received DESC;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, votes_received FROM election_results WHERE election_year = 2020 ORDER BY votes_received DESC, candidate_name ASC
SELECT * FROM election_results WHERE party_affiliation = 'Democratic' AND election_year BETWEEN 2016 AND 2020 ORDER BY election_year ASC
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, SUM(votes_received) AS total_votes FROM election_results GROUP BY candidate_name, party_affiliation HAVING total_votes > 5000 ORDER BY total_votes DESC
SELECT election_id, MAX(votes_received) AS max_votes FROM election_results GROUP BY election_id HAVING max_votes > 10000 ORDER BY max_votes DESC
SELECT DISTINCT party_affiliation FROM election_results ORDER BY party_affiliation ASC
SELECT * FROM election_results
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation FROM election_results WHERE votes_received > 1000
SELECT * FROM election_results ORDER BY votes_received DESC
SELECT election_year, COUNT(candidate_name) AS total_candidates FROM election_results GROUP BY election_year
SELECT party_affiliation, AVG(votes_received) AS average_votes FROM election_results GROUP BY party_affiliation ORDER BY average_votes DESC
SELECT * FROM election_results WHERE party_affiliation = 'Democratic' ORDER BY votes_received DESC;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, votes_received FROM election_results WHERE election_year = 2020 AND party_affiliation = 'Republican' ORDER BY votes_received ASC;
SELECT voter_id, age, region FROM voter_demographics WHERE gender = 'Female' AND region IN ('West', 'East') ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, SUM(votes_received) AS total_votes FROM election_results GROUP BY candidate_name, party_affiliation HAVING total_votes > 50000 ORDER BY total_votes DESC;

SELECT e.candidate_name, v.gender, v.region, v.voting_district FROM election_results e JOIN voter_demographics v ON e.election_id = v.voting_district WHERE e.party_affiliation = 'Independent' AND v.age >= 18 ORDER BY v.region, e.votes_received DESC;
SELECT * FROM election_results;
SELECT election_year, election_type, winning_party FROM election_results;
SELECT voter_id, voter_age, voter_gender, voter_location FROM voter_demographics;
SELECT candidate_name, candidate_party, candidate_age FROM candidate_data;
SELECT election_id, election_year, election_type, winning_party, voter_turnout FROM election_results;
SELECT * FROM election_results WHERE voter_turnout > 50000;
SELECT election_year, election_type FROM election_results WHERE winning_party='Red Party';
SELECT MAX(voter_age), MIN(voter_age), AVG(voter_age) FROM voter_demographics WHERE voter_location='City A';
SELECT candidate_name, candidate_age, candidate_gender FROM candidate_data WHERE candidate_party='Blue Party' ORDER BY candidate_age DESC;
SELECT election_year, SUM(voter_turnout) AS total_turnout FROM election_results GROUP BY election_year ORDER BY election_year DESC;
SELECT * FROM election_results;
SELECT candidate_name, votes_received FROM election_results ORDER BY votes_received DESC;
SELECT election_year, candidate_name FROM election_results WHERE election_year = 2020;
SELECT party_name, district_name FROM political_parties, voting_districts WHERE political_parties.party_id = 1 AND voting_districts.district_id = 3;

SELECT party_name, candidate_name, votes_received FROM election_results, political_parties, election_participants WHERE election_results.election_id = election_participants.election_id AND political_parties.party_id = election_participants.party_id;
SELECT * FROM election_results ORDER BY election_year DESC, votes_received ASC;
SELECT candidate_name, votes_received FROM election_results WHERE votes_received > 10000;

SELECT party_name, district_name FROM political_parties p INNER JOIN election_participants ep ON p.party_id = ep.party_id INNER JOIN voting_districts d ON ep.district_id = d.district_id ORDER BY party_name ASC, district_name DESC;

SELECT e.election_year, p.party_name, vr.candidate_name FROM election_participants ep JOIN election_results vr ON ep.election_id = vr.election_id JOIN political_parties p ON ep.party_id = p.party_id JOIN voting_districts d ON ep.district_id = d.district_id JOIN election_results e ON ep.election_id = e.election_id WHERE vr.votes_received > 5000 ORDER BY e.election_year DESC, p.party_name ASC;
SELECT MAX(votes_received) AS max_votes FROM election_results;
SELECT * FROM election_results;
SELECT candidate_name, total_votes FROM election_results WHERE election_year = 2020;
SELECT party_affiliation, COUNT(*) AS total_candidates FROM election_candidates GROUP BY party_affiliation;
SELECT district_name, state_name, region_name FROM election_districts ORDER BY state_name ASC;
SELECT party_name, party_leader FROM election_parties WHERE party_leader LIKE 'J%' ORDER BY party_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM election_results WHERE total_votes > 10000 ORDER BY election_year DESC;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, total_votes FROM election_results WHERE party_affiliation = 'Democratic' ORDER BY total_votes DESC;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, total_votes FROM election_results WHERE party_affiliation = 'Republican' ORDER BY total_votes DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation, election_year FROM election_results WHERE election_year = 2020 AND party_affiliation = 'Green Party' ORDER BY candidate_name ASC;

SELECT er.candidate_name, ep.party_name, ev.vote_timestamp FROM election_results er JOIN election_candidates ec ON er.candidate_name = ec.candidate_name JOIN election_votes ev ON er.election_id = ev.election_id JOIN election_parties ep ON ec.party_affiliation = ep.party_name ORDER BY ev.vote_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
